subject:  62)  doe motif work with x11r4? x11r5?

	motif 1.2 is base on x11r5.
	motif 1.1, avail in sourc form from osf as of august 1990, us 
the "vanilla" x11r4 intrins, where "vanilla" mean "with just a few 
patch"; the file fix-osf which osf distribut is obsolet by mit's patch 
15-17.  the file fix-osf-1.1.1 distribut with the 1.1.1 version or it 
subsequ modif need to be appli after mit fix-18, though.

	motif 1.1.1 to 1.1.3 will work with x11r5 if x11r5 is compil with
-dmotifbc; 1.1.4 and later should work with the vanilla r5, although there ar 
some known new geometri-manag problem.
	
