subject:  66)  where can i get a good file-selector widget?

	the free widget foundat set offer a fileselector widget, with 
separ directori path and file list window, and the filecomplet, which
ha emac-style file complet and ~ expans. 
	other avail file-requestor widget includ the xifileselector from 
iri softwar's book, the xdbx file-selector extract by david nedd 
(daven@wpi.wpi.edu), and the filenomin from the ax distribut.
