subject:  79)! where can i get an x-base paint/draw program?

	xpic is an object-orient draw program. it support multipl font 
style and size and variabl line width; there ar no rotat or zoom.
xpic is quit suitabl as an interact front-end to pic, though the 
xpic-format produc can be convert into postscript. (the latest version is 
on the r4 contrib tape in client/xpic.)

