draw program support compound object.  the xfig format can be convert 
to postscript or other format. recent version ar on the r5 contrib tape or 
on export in /contrib/r5fix (version 2.1.6 [11/92]).

        idraw support numer font and variou line style and arbitrari 
rotat. it support zoom and scroll and color draw and fill. the file 
format is a postscript dialect. it can import tiff file. distribut as a part
of the interview c++ toolkit (current releas 3.1, from 
interview.stanford.edu) .

